e minimal value $2$ of $\\delta$, we find out all the\noptimal cyclic $(r,2)$-LRCs of prime power lengths.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Apr 2023 07:30:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-04"}
